nodes.text: A female individual worked as a biologist on the Mid Rim world of Deminol during the reign of the Galactic Empire.

The biologist was introduced in "The Ride Of A Lifetime," a short companion narrative included in the 1994 sourcebook Creatures of the Galaxy, published by West End Games for Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game. The 2009 reference book The Essential Atlas placed the world in grid square L-17.
